{"id":806573,"date":[{"year":1989,"month":12,"day":28}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"笔会","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"140","ytitle":"","mtitle":"笔会","ftitle":"","authors":["赵丽宏"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"史勇伟　摄影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵丽宏　配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多象是地下崛起一座苍老的山峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周围的群山相形而年轻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月在他脸上风化出无数裂缝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漠然的神态注视人世风尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢乐和痛苦都已成为过去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲伤和忧愁也已深埋在心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有古老的希望未曾凝固"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她已化作高飞在天的雄鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要生命还在顽强地延续"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深邃的目光便注视着天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入9号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1989\\12\\89CS030701.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>史勇伟</FONT>"}]}